summary: An ordinance relating to zoning, establishing Use, Area, and Height Districts for the portions of Maple Leaf No. 1, Maple Leaf No. 2, and Yarbo Precincts, annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 73880 and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-139, 10-5 and 17-102, respectively.
